Joomla! enables you to build Web sites and powerful online applications.
 Joomla! is an award-winning content management system (CMS), which enables you to build Web sites and powerful online applications.
 
 With the cydia packages below you can use Joomla!: 
 - 'atv-lighttpd-php-mysql' for AppleTV
 - 'ios-lighttpd-php-mysql' for iPhone/iPad
 
 After the package installation please open Safari at your iOS Device and type in 'http://localhost/joomla'.
 
 The webinstaller will create files at /var/www/joomla with permissions for the user 'daemon:_www'.
  
 If you remove this package, please note that all content in /var/www/joomla will be deleted.
 
 If you would like to get more package information, please have a look at http://ios-webstack.tk . 
 
